        <bioghist>
            <p>Craig Wilson was a journalist for the Saratogian from 1976-1984. He later began working at USA Today where he was a featured columnist until leaving in 2013.

In 1996, Saratoga Springs Public Library Librarian, Jean Stamm approached several publishers for funding to publish a book of Wilson’s works. In 2002, Wilson published a book, “It’s the Little Things…”
</p>
